{"tid":2084561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"守孝期間 何猷君與奚夢瑤同遊迪士尼","createTime":"2020-06-29T10:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T10:11:00.000Z","uid":89543,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d55946e8601734e2d61e6be0f0ad720a714de773","tid":2084561,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"6月28日，有媒體從迪士尼樂園偶遇到何猷君、奚夢瑤夫婦。照片中，兩人遵守守孝期間要穿素色衣服的習俗，何猷君穿著黑色T恤，頭戴米老鼠頭飾，而奚夢瑤穿著黑色相間的T恤。<br />\n<br />\n在媒體采訪中，何猷君被問有沒有見過何猷邦，何猷君巧妙回應說今天是去迪士尼玩，不回答這些，希望大家能夠尊重家族，何猷君回應時一旁的奚夢瑤戴著口罩沒說一句話，一直低著頭跟在何猷君身邊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8j6iDX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8j6iDX4.jpg&h=764c7048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d34c3cf017d70fdd76328a620b2dd039b6734dd0","tid":2084561,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb620e400798cd5bab2e03a5d5a22ef86c76474","tid":2084561,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"呢個就似樣好多啦"},{"pid":"b04afab21f9abdfb31df0df7fab14a5becfd58b9","tid":2084561,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"Sorry借個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7qbYOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7qbYOf.jpg&h=a7fe3e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxDMNCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxDMNCG.jpg&h=d4c5779b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZ44zhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZ44zhG.jpg&h=0f9a99b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLJEoa2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLJEoa2.jpg&h=aba009ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/usN2kXK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht